    "A strong, steady stream of fuel squirts from both nozzles into the carburetor throat.",
    "Only a weak dribble or no fuel squirts from the nozzles.",
    "Fuel squirts from only one nozzle.",
    "Fuel is visibly dripping or pooling in the carburetor throat before the pedal is pressed."
  ],
